      <title>谷歌因应用商店是否非法垄断而支付7亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2023/12/19/1220202154/google-to-pay-700-million-in-case-over-whether-its-app-store-is-an-illegal-monop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[与数十个州达成的协议解决了一项诉讼，该诉讼声称谷歌通过其 Google Play 商店从事反竞争行为，这是大多数人在 Android 设备上下载应用程序的方式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2023/12/19/1220202154/google-to-pay-700-million-in-case-over-whether-its-app-store-is-an-illegal-monop</guid>
