      <title>数千人从附近城镇撤离数周后，冰岛一座火山爆发</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2023/12/18/1220183273/a-volcano-in-iceland-erupts-weeks-after-thousands-were-evacuated-from-a-nearby-t</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格林达维克地区的强烈地震活动损坏了房屋并引发了人们对即将爆发的担忧，警方于 11 月疏散了格林达维克。官员们表示，岩浆可能会继续朝这个方向发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2023/12/18/1220183273/a-volcano-in-iceland-erupts-weeks-after-thousands-were-evacuated-from-a-nearby-t</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 03:03:04 GMT</pubDate>
