    <item>
      <title>中国西部地震已造成100多人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2023/12/18/1220173525/earthquake-rattles-western-china-killing-at-least-111-people</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官方通讯社新华社称，此次地震震级为 6.2 级。据报道，山区的水、电、交通、通讯和其他基础设施遭到破坏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2023/12/18/1220173525/earthquake-rattles-western-china-killing-at-least-111-people</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 01:52:54 GMT</pubDate>
